,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca s\u1eafp c\u1ea3i t\u1ed5 s\u00e2n Camp Nou</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarcelona \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh quy\u1ec1n th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tu b\u1ed5 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u00e1c quan ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 ph\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh cho Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p s\u00e2n Camp Nou. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Blaugrana khi h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi t\u1edbi 600 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac l\u1ea1i m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi l\u00ean H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh quy\u1ec1n x\u1ee9 x\u1ee9 Catalonia. V\u1ec1 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u00e0y, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Josep Maria Bartomeu cho bi\u1ebft: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a CLB nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong khu v\u1ef1c v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Barcelona.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ke hoach Barca nang cap san Camp Nou duoc phe duyet hinh anh\" title=\"K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00ea duy\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/san-Camp-Nou.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p s\u00e2n Camp Nou m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng g\u00ec CLB v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Camp Nou s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e9p k\u00edn cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edf v\u00e0 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang, trong m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian xanh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh tu b\u1ed5 s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u1ee7a Barca d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra trong 5 n\u0103m t\u1edbi. S\u1eafp t\u1edbi, Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p s\u00e2n Camp Nou, c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf c\u1ee7a CLB v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh xung quanh. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd cho x\u00e2y m\u1edbi s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i B v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao ngo\u00e0i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi ti\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u00e2n Camp Nou s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u00e1i che, \u0111\u1ee7 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho kho\u1ea3ng 105 ngh\u00ecn ch\u1ed7. Barca c\u0169ng ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh tu s\u1eeda c\u1ed5ng v\u00e0o, khu v\u1ef1c VIP. H\u1ecd cho x\u00e2y th\u00eam c\u00e1c c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed3 l\u01b0u ni\u1ec7m v\u00e0 c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng kh\u00e1c. M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1ng l\u00ean v\u1edbi 12 ngh\u00ecn ch\u1ed7 ng\u1ed3i, n\u01a1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ed5, b\u00f3ng n\u00e9m, kh\u00fac c\u00f4n c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i futsal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"san Nou Camp moi\" title=\"san Nou Camp moi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/san-Nou-Camp-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M\u00f4 h\u00ecnh s\u00e2n Camp Nou m\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Barca s\u1ebd di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n m\u1edbi mang t\u00ean huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i CLB, Estadi Johan Cruyff v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9a 6 ngh\u00ecn ch\u1ed7 ng\u1ed3i, c\u00e1ch s\u00e2n ch\u00ednh Camp Nou h\u01a1n 8 km. C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. S\u00e2n Johan Cruyff d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111i v\u00e0o ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng chi ph\u00ed c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u00e0y r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 600 tri\u1ec7u euro. Barca d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn chi ph\u00ed b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch b\u00e1n quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1edbi cho nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Barcelona tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/barca-bi-roma-loai-khoi-champions-league-khong-dep-khong-co-quyen-184-184089.html\">Barca b\u1ecb Roma \u201c\u0111\u00e1 bay\u201d kh\u1ecfi Champions League: Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nhung-dieu-se-xay-ra-sau-tham-bai-lich-su-cua-barca-184-184014.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra sau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/quan-diem-barca-phai-cam-on-nguoi-ban-tot-roma-184-183997.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: Barca ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t Roma</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thay-gi-sau-man-nguoc-dong-khong-tuong-cua-roma-truoc-barca-184-183976.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Roma tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-bao-gio-messi-thanh-liet-si-cua-barca-180-183894.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Bao gi\u1edd Messi th\u00e0nh \u201cli\u1ec7t s\u0129\u201d c\u1ee7a Barca?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>