0e3 ghi t\u1edbi 39 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho The Kop ch\u1ec9 sau 44 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Salah kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Real Madrid. Trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-bao-chi-de-so-huu-mohamed-salah-172-182955.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Salah</strong></span>. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia \u0111ang r\u1ee5c r\u1ecbch c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ngay trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp phat bieu ve tuong lai Salah day lac quan hinh anh\" title=\"Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Salah \u0111\u1ea7y l\u1ea1c quan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-Salah-day-lac-quan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Salah \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi Mohamed Salah. Trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n v\u1edbi t\u1edd Bild, Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Salah m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1 l\u1ea1c quan. Theo \u00f4ng, s\u1ed1 11 c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111ang \u1edf trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng. \u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Salah c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng phong c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh\u201d, Klopp n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSalah \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n trong c\u1ea3 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League, gi\u00fap <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-nhan-man-city-12-liverpool-184-183991.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Man City chung cu\u1ed9c 5-1</strong></span>. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u1ea1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y (4-3 h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp va Salah cua Liverpool\" title=\"Klopp va Salah cua Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-salah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\">Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Salah \u0111\u1ea7y l\u1ea1c quan<br>\r\n            </span></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p 3 l\u1ea7n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Klopp v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh cho Guardiola s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9: \u201c\u1ede m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng cho \u00f4ng \u1ea5y\u201d, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cT\u1ea1i Barcelona, Bayern Munich v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 Man City. N\u1ebfu Guardiola kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t th\u00edch xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-can-4-ban-hop-dong-chat-luong-de-thanh-cong-vao-mua-toi-172-184050.html\">Liverpool c\u1ea7n 4 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/pep-guardiola-va-liverpool-dung-truoc-an-phat-cua-uefa-184-184059.html\">Pep Guardiola v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a UEFA</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/van-gaal-phat-bieu-ve-liverpool-sau-tran-thang-184-184041.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Man City, Liverpool v\u1eabn b\u1ecb c\u1ef1u HLV M.U xem th\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-man-city-12-liverpool-184-184038.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/gabriel-jesus-phat-bieu-sau-tran-man-city-vs-liverpool-184-184035.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Man City ch\u1ec9 ra b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1102","checkdouble":"184115"},{"date":"18:31 12/04","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Man City quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i danh ti\u1ebfng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/tien-dao-gabriel-jesus-phat-bieu-ve-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration: