ze:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hazard lung l\u1ea1c b\u1edfi Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp n\u0103m 2012, Eden Hazard lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a CLB m\u00f9a n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 \u00fd c\u1ee7a anh. Chelsea ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League c\u00f2n ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt trong vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a sau ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea1n h\u1eb9p h\u01a1n. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/real-va-chelsea-sap-co-tan-binh-khung-172-183124.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ve v\u00e3n Hazard</strong></span>, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng b\u1ecb lung l\u1ea1c. Vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi trong d\u1ea3i ng\u00e2n h\u00e0 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Desailly khuyen Chelsea ban Hazard ngay he nay hinh anh\" title=\"Desailly khuy\u00ean Chelsea b\u00e1n Hazard ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/13/Desailly-khuyen-Chelsea-ban-Hazard-ngay-he-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hazard \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/hazard-tiep-tuc-tu-choi-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-chelsea-172-181431.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Hazard t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea</strong></span> li\u00ean t\u1ee5c. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng, anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng giao k\u00e8o ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2020.</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean b\u00e1n Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Marcel Desailly tin r\u1eb1ng Chelsea ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Eden Hazard trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u201cRoman Abramovich r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi Chelsea b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 Champions League. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi\u201d, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng 6 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i cho Chelsea (1998 t\u1edbi 2004) n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard vs Barca\" title=\"Hazard vs Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/21/ly-do-chelsea-ban-eden-hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Desailly khuy\u00ean Chelsea b\u00e1n Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu Chelsea b\u00e1n Hazard, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c. Willian c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ebf vai. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u1edbi m\u1ebb\u201d, Desailly khuy\u00ean Chelsea b\u00e1n Hazard nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho r\u1eb1ng CLB c\u0169 n\u00ean gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/conte-o-lai-chelsea-mua-giai-toi-172-183710.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Conte, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</strong></span>. \u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen thay \u0111\u1ed5i HLV v\u00e0 gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u1ecd n\u00ean gi\u1eef HLV v\u00e0 xem x\u00e9t chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 4 t\u1edbi 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi\u201d, Desailly n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat v\u00e0 Chelsea kh\u00f4ng mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1i Chelsea m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a HLV Conte. H\u1ecd n\u00ean ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi anh \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/drinkwater-co-the-roi-chelsea-chi-sau-mot-mua-giai-172-184108.html\">Drinkwater c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-mua-alvaro-morata-cua-chelsea-172-183915.html\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u \u201cbom x\u1ecbt\u201d Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/psg-mua-trung-ve-alderweireld-197-183423.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u201cgi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u\u201d sao Tottenham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-cua-newcastle-172-183287.html\">Chelsea chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Newcastle</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-mua-toby-alderweireld-cung-mu-va-barca-172-183178.html\">V\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng, Chelsea tuy\u00ean chi\u1ebfn M.U v\u00e0 Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1100","checkdouble":"184119"},{"date":"22:40 12/04","title":"Pochettino b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Kane","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/pochettino-bao-ve-hanh-dong-doi-ban-thang-cua-kane.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6p