c-dua-vua-pha-luoi-172-183860.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Harry Kane cho r\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</strong></span>. Khi Eriksen \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1eaft m\u1eb7t. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh c\u00f2n th\u1ec1 c\u00f3 con g\u00e1i m\u00ecnh r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Stoke.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino phat bieu ve Kane va ban thang truoc Stoke hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kane v\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Stoke h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Harry-Kane-va-Eriksen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tranh c\u00e3i Kane hay Eriksen ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Stoke</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea5y, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m sau khi nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Harry Kane. Anh thu h\u1eb9p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi l\u00e0 Mohamed Salah xu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 4 b\u00e0n (25 so v\u1edbi 29). Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cong-dong-mang-thi-nhau-troll-viec-harry-kane-doi-ban-thang-172-184088.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Kane b\u1ecb c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u</strong></span>.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nPochettino b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Kane</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c v\u1eeba qua, HLV Mauricio Pochettino tin r\u1eb1ng Harry Kane \u0111\u00e3 trung th\u1ef1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u00e0nh cho Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pochettino bi soc sau that bai truoc Juventus\" title=\"Pochettino b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/8/psg-va-real-gap-kho-vu-hlv-tottenham.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kane \u0111\u1ea7y tin t\u01b0\u1edfng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f2n b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 n\u00f3. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3, Harry n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng vai ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d, Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kane tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cHarry r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh th\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i d\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 l\u00ean tr\u00ean m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m ai ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, t\u00f4i quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Harry kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ghi b\u00e0n, Christian n\u00f3i \u1ed5n th\u00f4i, kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec. Nh\u01b0ng chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec to t\u00e1t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Harry Kane tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cong-dong-mang-thi-nhau-troll-viec-harry-kane-doi-ban-thang-172-184088.html\">C\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng thi nhau troll vi\u1ec7c Harry Kane \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/doi-lai-cong-bang-harry-kane-bi-doi-thu-salah-mia-mai-172-184083.html\">\u0110\u00f2i l\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, Harry Kane b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Salah m\u1ec9a mai</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/kane-tuyen-chien-salah-trong-cuoc-dua-vua-pha-luoi-172-183860.html\">Kane tuy\u00ean chi\u1ebfn Salah trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-stoke-vs-tottenham-21h00-ngay-74-premier-league-201718-372-183726.html\">Stoke 1-2 Tottenham (KT): Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Spurs th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-nhan-tin-cuc-vui-tu-harry-kane-172-183672.html\">Tottenham nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c vui t\u1eeb Harry Kane</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1099","checkdouble":"184124"},{"date":"00:35 13/04","title":"Pogba l\u00e0 thi\