u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c nh\u01b0 \u1edf Juventus, th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ruc-sang-tran-derby-pogba-van-bi-nguoi-mu-chi-trich-172-183773.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Pogba ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</strong></span> t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin M.U v\u00e0 HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n Pogba r\u1ed9 l\u00ean tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o. Chuy\u1ec7n nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n hi\u1ebfm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Christophe Dugarry phat bieu ve Pogba kem nhac nho hinh anh\" title=\"Christophe Dugarry ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pogba k\u00e8m nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Pogba-cua-M.U.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pogba ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u g\u00f3p \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi t\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/de-tro-thanh-so-1-pogba-can-phai-lam-dieu-nay-172-183814.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Frank Lampard khuy\u00ean Pogba b\u1edbt r\u01b0\u1eddm r\u00e0</strong></span>. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Christophe Dugarry ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pogba m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1998 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh sao M.U c\u00f3 t\u00e0i nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7n tu d\u01b0\u1ee1ng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i h\u00e0nh tinh, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i phi\u1ec1n n\u00e3o. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m g\u1ea5p tr\u0103m l\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thi\u00ean t\u00e0i, nh\u01b0ng khi n\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh? T\u1eeb khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1t khao t\u1eebng c\u00f3 \u1edf Juventus.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"cuu tien dao Dugarry\" title=\"cuu tien dao Dugarry\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/cuu-tien-dao-Dugarry.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Dugarry ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pogba v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd c\u1ee7a Dugarry kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i \u00e1m ch\u1ec9 Pogba \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. T\u1eeb c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o l\u1ed9ng l\u1eaby r\u1ed3i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c s\u1eb7c s\u1ee1, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dugarry, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/pogba-bi-huyen-thoai-mu-dan-mat-172-183110.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Bryan Robson t\u1eebng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Pogba</strong></span> c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-muon-tay-pogba-de-chieu-mo-ngoi-sao-nay-trong-he-toi-172-183972.html\">Mourinho m\u01b0\u1ee3n tay Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y trong h\u00e8 t\u1edbi?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/toa-sang-o-derby-manchester-pogba-van-that-vong-tran-tre-172-183889.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf derby Manchester, v\u00ec sao Pogba v\u1eabn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sanchez-noi-gi-voi-pogba-truoc-tran-derby-172-183865.html\">Sanchez n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1edbi Pogba tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn derby?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/de-tro-thanh-so-1-pogba-can-phai-lam-dieu-nay-172-183814.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1, Pogba c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-gui-psg-pogba-martial-neymar-172-183797.html\">MU g\u1eedi PSG: Pogba + Martial = Neymar?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ruc-sang-tran-derby-pogba-van-bi-nguo