ella Roccuzzo \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Ngay sau khi Messi v\u00e0 Barca thua s\u1ed1c Roma 0-3 v\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League, Antonella b\u1ecb bi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c fan qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a Barca gi\u1eadn c\u00e1, ch\u00e9m th\u1edbt.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e0nh r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ee9c lang qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Antonella v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Roma. \u0110\u00e0nh r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u fan cu\u1ed3ng ch\u1eedi r\u1ee7a Messi. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00e1i ngang \u1edf ch\u1ed7, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i c\u1ee9 nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Instagram c\u1ee7a Antonella m\u00e0 t\u1ed5ng s\u1ec9 v\u1ea3. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u00f5 l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u0103ng \u1ea3nh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00ean Instagram, Antonella ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n khoe \u1ea3nh qu\u00fd t\u1eed m\u1edbi sinh c\u00f3 t\u00ean Ciro. Th\u1ebf m\u00e0 c\u00f4 v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn \u201cg\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e1\u201d ki\u1ec3u: \u201cTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Messi. Gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 \u0111i cho r\u1ed3i\u201d, \u201cMessi h\u1ebft th\u1eddi r\u1ed3i. B\u1ea3o anh ta treo gi\u00e0y \u0111i\u201d hay \u201cCh\u1ed3ng c\u00f4 b\u1ecb l\u00e0m sao th\u1ebf!\u201d. \u1ea4y l\u00e0 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u ch\u1eedi th\u1ec1, v\u0103ng n\u1ecd v\u0103ng kia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1m th\u1eddi ch\u01b0a th\u1ea5y Antonella \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 n\u00e0o. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5 th\u00eam d\u1ea7u v\u00e0o l\u1eeda. C\u00f3 fan th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Antonella khi v\u00ed von: \u201cPh\u00eda sau sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef, c\u00f2n ph\u00eda sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef v\u1ea1 l\u00e2y\u201d.</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1097","checkdouble":"184099"},{"date":"15:51 12/04","title":"Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e1ng 3 V-League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/18/xuan-truong-nhan-giai-thuong-thang-3-vleague.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;c