none\" alt=\"Sau hieu ung U23, bong da Viet Nam co nha tai tro moi hinh anh\" title=\"Sau hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng U23, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/8d129e063bc8b80a9fb182dfe9116f78.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 m\u1edbi Coca-Cola&nbsp;</em><i>trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2018-19</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, c\u00f4ng ty Coca-Cola s\u1ebd c\u1ea5p kinh ph\u00ed h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb U16, U19 nam, n\u1eef chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tham d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khu v\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c trong n\u0103m 2018.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda Coca-Cola c\u0169ng cam k\u1ebft s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam qu\u1ed1c gia tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft ASIAN Cup 2019, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng tham v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Trung Qu\u1ed1c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb t\u1ea1i bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5, \u00f4ng L\u00ea Ho\u00e0i Anh - T\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd VFF nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh: &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t l\u00e0n gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi, l\u00e0m n\u1ee9c l\u00f2ng NHM v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng cao tinh th\u1ea7n d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chung, tinh th\u1ea7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i ri\u00eang.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n, VFF s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadp trung v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn lao h\u01a1n, trong \u0111\u00f3 World Cup c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh, \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 thi\u1ebft th\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Coca-Cola cho n\u1ec1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam-c168-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span>, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u00eam ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao m\u1edbi&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Coca-Cola, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Sanket Ray c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c n\u00e0y: &ldquo;C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00e0ng h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi World Cup, l\u1ec5 k\u00fd k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c c\u00f9ng VFF ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Coca-Cola Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3, \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bxh-fifa-thang-42018-dt-viet-nam-tang-truong-manh-168-184106.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/bxh-fifa-thang-42018-dt-viet-nam-tang-truong-manh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bxh-fifa-thang-42018-dt-viet-nam-tang-truong-manh-168-184106.html\">BXH FIFA th\u00e1ng 4/2018: \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ea1nh</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Jordan t\u1ea1i V\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ea1nh tr\u00ean BXH FIFA th\u00e1ng 4/2018.</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1094","checkdouble":"184109"},{"date":"16:59 12/04","title":"B\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c ra tay c\u1ee9u T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn kh\u1ecfi \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a VFF","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/4/bau-duc-ra-tay-cuu-tang-tien-khoi-an-phat-cua-vff.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left