champions-league-201718-372-184054.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Juventus v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-3</span> sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League n\u0103m nay. K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng b\u1ecb d\u1eabn 3-0 sau tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 Juve c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i Bernabeu. Nh\u01b0ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a CR7 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eadt l\u1ea1i su\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1 cho Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Zidane s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 1 trong 3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Liverpool, Bayern Munich ho\u1eb7c AS Roma. Bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League n\u0103m nay s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ramos nguy co bi treo gio o ban ket C1 sau man cai co voi Allegri hinh anh\" title=\"Ramos nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1 sau m\u00e0n c\u00e3i c\u1ecd v\u1edbi Allegri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/ramos-nguy-co-vang-mat-o-ban-ket-c1-sau-man-cai-co-voi-allegri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ramos xu\u1ed1ng th\u1eb3ng khu v\u1ef1c hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 tranh c\u00e3i v\u1edbi Allegri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ramos \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Do b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n tranh c\u00e3i \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng m\u1ea1nh khi \u0111i v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ea7m s\u00e2n Bernarbeu. T\u1edd Marca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 va ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1ea9u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 Sergio Ramos \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lao v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 tranh c\u00e3i v\u1edbi HLV Allegri. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Bernabeu, Ramos ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p theo d\u00f5i tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2. V\u00e0 h\u00e0nh vi qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 kh\u00e1c.</em><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/vazquez-noi-gi-ve-qua-penalty-gay-tranh-cai-o-tran-gap-juventus-184-184087.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/vazquez-noi-gi-ve-qua-penalty-gay-tranh-cai-o-tran-gap-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/vazquez-noi-gi-ve-qua-penalty-gay-tranh-cai-o-tran-gap-juventus-184-184087.html\">Th\u1ea7n t\u00e0i Vazquez n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Juventus?</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1eabn t\u1edbi qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t penalty cho Real, \u2018ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c\u2019 Lucas Vazquez \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh vi t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng t\u1eebng gi\u00e1ng xu\u1ed1ng Real Madrid. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Xabi Alonso \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 1 tr\u1eadn v\u00ec ch\u1ea1y xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale khi \u0111ang l\u0129nh \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2013/14.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Steven Gerrard c\u1ee7a Liverpool cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ramos \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Juventus v\u1eeba qua \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn t\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi m\u1ea5t Ramos, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Real t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 v\u00f4 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c. \u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Real l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng. V\u00e0 Juventus li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o c\u1ed9t sau khi\u1ebfn Real kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn Real vs Juventus:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/dan-sao-real-madrid-an-mung-sau-man-hut-chet-truoc-juventus-329-184097.html\">D\u00e0n sao Real Madrid \u0103n m\u1eebng sau m\u00e0n h\u00fat ch\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-real-madrid-13-juventus-nga-mu-truoc-nhung-chien-binh-cua-allegri-184-184090.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Real Madrid 1-3 Juventus: Ng\u1ea3 m\u0169 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh c\u1ee7a Allegri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/zidane-phat-bieu-ve-buffon-va-tam-the-do-184-184080.html\">Zidane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ee7a Buffon</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/buffon-phan-ung-trong-tai-tran-real-vs-juventus-co-the-thong-cam-duoc-184-184079.html\">Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Buffon tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-real-madrid-13-juventus-nhung-cam-xuc-trai-chieu-184-184077.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Real Madrid 1-3 Juventus: Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/dua-real-vao-ban-ket-champions-league-cristiano-ronaldo-noi-gi-184-184074.html\">\u0110\u01b0a Real v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League, Cristiano Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/quyet-dinh-tang-penalty-cho-real-madrid-la-chinh-xac-184-184071.html\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eb7ng penalty cho Real Madrid l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hlv-juventus-neu-chung-toi-vao-ban-ket-cung-hoan-toan-xung-dang-184-184073.html\">HLV Juventus: \u201cN\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng\u201d</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1091","checkdouble":"184100"},{"date":"15:10 12/04","title":"H\u1eadu t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18: Khi ranh gi\u1edbi \u00f4ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u0